        <SUBJECT>
          Loan servicing.
        </SUBJECT>
        <P>
          Loans will be serviced as a Non-program loan in accordance with 
          <aref type='CFR'>
            7 CFR part 
            <subref title='7' part='766' tq='N'>
              766
            </subref>
          </aref>
          . If the loan is not repaid as agreed and default occurs, servicing
          will proceed in accordance with 
          <aref type='CFR'>
            7 CFR part 
            <subref title='7' part='766' tq='N'>
              766
            </subref>
          </aref>
          , subpart H.
        </P>
        <CITA>
          [
          <aref type='FREGIST'>
            72 FR 64121
          </aref>
          , Nov. 15, 2007]
        </CITA>
      </contents>
    </section>
